            <!-- <com:USSGLTransactionCode>?</com:USSGLTransactionCode> -->
            <!-- <com:VATTaxId>?</com:VATTaxId> -->

            <!-- <com:ReferenceNumber>313505</com:ReferenceNumber> -->
            <com:ReferenceId>300000257792547</com:ReferenceId>

            <!-- <com:BankAccountNumber>?</com:BankAccountNumber> -->
            <!-- <com:InterfaceToBudgeting>?</com:InterfaceToBudgeting> -->
            <!-- <com:InterfaceFailureReason>?</com:InterfaceFailureReason> -->
            <!-- <com:MiscellaneousReceiptFLEXVA>
               <mis:CashReceiptId>?</mis:CashReceiptId>
               <mis:__FLEX_Context>?</mis:__FLEX_Context>
               <mis:__FLEX_Context_DisplayValue>?</mis:__FLEX_Context_DisplayValue>
               <mis:_FLEX_NumOfSegments>?</mis:_FLEX_NumOfSegments>
            </com:MiscellaneousReceiptFLEXVA> -->
            <com:MiscellaneousReceiptDistributionsService>
               <!-- <com:Amount currencyCode="USD">?</com:Amount> -->
               <com:ConcatSegment>101.10.41000.120.235.000</com:ConcatSegment>
               <com:Percent>50</com:Percent>
               <!-- <com:MiscReceiptDistServiceDFF>
                  <mis1:MiscCashDistributionId>?</mis1:MiscCashDistributionId>
                  <mis1:__FLEX_Context>?</mis1:__FLEX_Context>

               </com:MiscReceiptDistServiceDFF> -->

            <com:MiscellaneousReceiptDistributionsService>
               <!-- <com:Amount currencyCode="USD">?</com:Amount> -->

               <com:Percent>50</com:Percent>
            </com:MiscellaneousReceiptDistributionsService>

<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:typ="http://xmlns.oracle.com/apps/financials/receivables/receipts/shared/miscellaneousReceiptService/commonService/types/" xmlns:com="http://xmlns.oracle.com/apps/financials/receivables/receipts/shared/miscellaneousReceiptService/commonService/" xmlns:mis="http://xmlns.oracle.com/apps/financials/receivables/receipts/shared/model/flex/MiscellaneousReceiptDff/" xmlns:mis1="http://xmlns.oracle.com/apps/flex/financials/receivables/receipts/shared/miscellaneousReceiptService/commonService/MiscReceiptDistServiceDff/">
   <soapenv:Header/>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <typ:createMiscellaneousReceipt> /* 200 OK Created cash_receipt_id 453422 with all expected DFF values */
         <typ:miscellaneousReceipt>
            <com:ReceiptNumber>BDS016USDMisc</com:ReceiptNumber>
            <com:Amount currencyCode="USD">100.00</com:Amount>
            <com:AnticipatedClearingDate>2025-03-31</com:AnticipatedClearingDate>
            <!-- <com:CashReceiptId>?</com:CashReceiptId> -->
            <com:Comments>SOAP Misc Receipt Upload</com:Comments>
            <com:CurrencyCode>USD</com:CurrencyCode>
            <com:DepositDate>2025-03-31</com:DepositDate>
            <!-- <com:DocumentSequenceValue>?</com:DocumentSequenceValue> -->
            <!-- <com:ExchangeDate>?</com:ExchangeDate> -->
            <!-- <com:ExchangeRate>?</com:ExchangeRate> -->
            <!-- <com:ExchangeRateType>?</com:ExchangeRateType> -->
            <com:GlDate>2025-03-31</com:GlDate>
            <!-- Check (Directly/No Remit) -->
            <com:ReceiptMethodId>300000047311659</com:ReceiptMethodId>
            <!-- US1 Business Unit -->
            <com:OrgId>300000046987012</com:OrgId>
            <!-- Miscellaneous Cash -->
            <!-- <com:ReceivableActivityName>?</com:ReceivableActivityName> -->
            <com:ReceivablesTransactionId>300000047295465</com:ReceivablesTransactionId> /* Miscellaneous Cash */
            <!-- <com:PaymentTransactionExtensionId>?</com:PaymentTransactionExtensionId> -->
            <com:MiscellaneousPaymentSource>Solicitor Deposit</com:MiscellaneousPaymentSource>
            <com:ReceiptDate>2025-03-31</com:ReceiptDate>
            <!-- cash_receipt_id = 397412 -->
            <com:RemittanceBankAccountId>300000047314453</com:RemittanceBankAccountId>
            <!-- <com:TaxCode>M4A_TAX_RATE</com:TaxCode>             -->
            <!-- <com:TaxCode>GB VAT TAX STANDARD RATE</com:TaxCode> -->
            <!-- <com:TaxRate>1.5</com:TaxRate> -->
            <!-- <com:UserCurrencyCode>?</com:UserCurrencyCode> -->
            <!-- <com:UserExchangeRateType>?</com:UserExchangeRateType> -->
            <!-- <com:USSGLTransactionCode>?</com:USSGLTransactionCode> -->
            <!-- <com:VATTaxId>?</com:VATTaxId> -->
            <!-- <com:TaxAmount currencyCode="AUD">15</com:TaxAmount> -->
            <!-- <com:ReceiptMethodName>?</com:ReceiptMethodName> -->
            <!-- <com:ReferenceType>CREDIT_MEMO</com:ReferenceType> -->
            <!-- <com:ReferenceNumber>313505</com:ReferenceNumber> -->
            <!-- <com:ReferenceId>300000257792547</com:ReferenceId> --> /* custmer_trx_id of the CREDIT MEMO */
            <!-- <com:BankAccountName>?</com:BankAccountName> -->
            <!-- <com:BankAccountNumber>?</com:BankAccountNumber> -->
            <!-- <com:InterfaceToBudgeting>?</com:InterfaceToBudgeting> -->
            <!-- <com:InterfaceFailureReason>?</com:InterfaceFailureReason> -->
            <com:MiscellaneousReceiptFLEXVA xsi:type="mis:More4appsReceipts">
               <mis:__FLEX_Context>M4A_RECEIPTS</mis:__FLEX_Context> 
               <mis:printedReceipt>Yes</mis:printedReceipt> 
               <mis:receiptSource>Reception Counter</mis:receiptSource> 
            </com:MiscellaneousReceiptFLEXVA>
            <com:MiscellaneousReceiptDistributionsService>
               <!-- <com:Amount currencyCode="USD">50</com:Amount> -->
               <com:ConcatSegment>101.10.41000.120.235.000</com:ConcatSegment>
               <com:Percent>24.5</com:Percent>
               <com:MiscReceiptDistServiceDFF xsi:type="mis1:ReceptionReceipt">  /* If the xsi:type is missing the Context DFF segments will fail to upload */
                  <!-- <mis1:MiscCashDistributionId>?</mis1:MiscCashDistributionId> -->
                  <mis1:receiptSource>Casual</mis1:receiptSource>
                  <mis1:receiptLocation>Hamilton Library</mis1:receiptLocation>
                  <mis1:__FLEX_Context>Reception_Receipt</mis1:__FLEX_Context>
                  <mis1:purchaserType>Reader</mis1:purchaserType>
                  <mis1:paymentDateChar>09-Jun-2025</mis1:paymentDateChar>
               </com:MiscReceiptDistServiceDFF>
            </com:MiscellaneousReceiptDistributionsService>
            <com:MiscellaneousReceiptDistributionsService>
               <!-- <com:Amount currencyCode="USD">50</com:Amount> -->
               <com:ConcatSegment>101.10.41000.120.311.000</com:ConcatSegment>
               <com:Percent>75.5</com:Percent>
               <com:MiscReceiptDistServiceDFF xsi:type="mis1:BankStmtReceipt"> /* If the xsi:type is missing the Context DFF segments will fail to upload */
                  <mis1:receiptSource>Westpac</mis1:receiptSource>
                  <mis1:receiptLocation>Bank Feed</mis1:receiptLocation>
                  <mis1:__FLEX_Context>Bank_Stmt_Receipt</mis1:__FLEX_Context>
                  <mis1:bankStmtNumber>09062025</mis1:bankStmtNumber> 
                  <mis1:bankStmtDateChar>09-Jun-2025</mis1:bankStmtDateChar> 
               </com:MiscReceiptDistServiceDFF>
            </com:MiscellaneousReceiptDistributionsService>
         </typ:miscellaneousReceipt>
      </typ:createMiscellaneousReceipt>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
